## Code Example
```javascript
// Pseudo-Beam DoFn skeleton for schema validation
class ValidateSchema extends DoFn {
  processElement(context) {
    const record = context.element;
    // load canonical schema from GCS
    // validate fields, types, requireds
    if (valid(record)) {
      context.output(record);
    } else {
      context.output(NOT_VALID, record);
    }
  }
}
```

